snippet.title: Echoes of Dread - Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
#horrorgame #horror #indiehorror #scarymansion #echoesofdread #reapergs

Hi! This is a showcase of the teaser for my indie horror game Echoes of Dread. Explore a haunted mansion, solve puzzles, and experience chilling scares as you uncover the dark story behind it all.

Wishlist on Steam now!
